@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_juulpl(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = (v2 * (0.99 + 0.66))
    v2 = (0.60 / (wp.cos(v2 + 0.20) / tmp))
    v0 = v2
    v1 = wp.exp((tmp * wp.cos(v2 + 0.08)))
    v0 = wp.cos(0.54)
    v2 = tmp
    data[tid] = v0
